Description:
Annotation on the envelope: "Rubens Pompa Introitus Ferdinandi" addressed (inside) to "Herrn Prof. Dr. Hans Gerhard Evers Lehrstühl und Institut für Kunstgeschichte, Technische Hochschule D-61 Darmstadt D.B.R."

  • Photos of old Antwerp maps and of an engraved 'Belva Marina'
  • Reproductions of engraved triumphal arches, 'Neptune Calming The Waves' and 'Meeting of King Ferdinand of Hungary and the Cardinal-Infante Ferdinand of Spain at Nördlingen'
  • Photocopies of the chatpter "XXIII. Pompa introitus Ferdinandi"
